This paper deals with the problem of optimizing the transmission time of packets in an energy harvesting system, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses power and rate allocation, which are topics in control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions an iterative algorithm, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG).
